Class SessionAssistantTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • SessionAssistantTests
  • public class SessionAssistantTests
extends java.lang.Object
    These are the test cases for the SessionAssistant and for componenets that have functionality that is integrated with the SessionAssitant. --- HELP: My SessionAssistantTests are failing, why? --- --- Common Causes --- 1. Improper database credentials. Verify that the hibernate properties file has the correct credentials to your database. 2. Relic test data. Verify that the database does not contain old generated test data. 3. Max hourly questions limit reached for user. Wait an hour and increase the max questions limit for your MySQL user.
